Package: robstore
Title: Object Storage via the Rust object_store Crate
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Michael", "Sumner", , "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R bindings to the Rust object_store crate, providing a uniform
    interface to local filesystems and (later) cloud object stores including
    S3, GCS, and Azure. Phase 1 supports local filesystem and in-memory stores
    only; cloud backends and async I/O are planned.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
URL: https://github.com/mdsumner/robstore
BugReports: https://github.com/mdsumner/robstore/issues
